[Name] Artistic Style
[Summary] A lightweight automatic formatter for C, C++, C# and Java source code
[Description] Artistic Style is a source code indenter, formatter, and beautifier for the C, C++, C# and Java programming languages.  It can be used from a command line, or it can be incorporated as classes in another C++ program.
[License] GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL), version 2.1
[Homepage] https://astyle.sourceforge.net/
